---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for DOGBREEDAGE. We respect your privacy and do not collect any personal data."
>
  <section class="container-custom py-10 sm:py-16 md:py-24 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-0 sm:px-1">
      <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "WebPage",
        "name": "Privacy Policy",
        "description": "Privacy Policy for DOGBREEDAGE. We respect your privacy and do not collect any personal data.",
        "url": "https://dogbreedage.com/privacy-policy",
        "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "DOGBREEDAGE", "url": "https://dogbreedage.com" },
        "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "DOGBREEDAGE", "url": "https://dogbreedage.com" },
        "datePublished": "2025-01-15",
        "dateModified": new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]
      })} />
      <span class="inline-block text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--text-faint)] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-[var(--border-default)] mb-4 sm:mb-6">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-6 sm:mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-7 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Effective Date:</strong> January 1, 2025</p>
        <p>
          At DOGBREEDAGE, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          Our calculator operates entirely in your browser. Any data you enter — your dog's name, breed size, and age — is processed locally using JavaScript on your device. We do not store, transmit, or have access to this information.
        </p>
        <p>
          We use Google Analytics to understand general website traffic patterns. Google Analytics collects anonymized data such as pages visited, time spent on site, and browser type. This data cannot be used to identify you personally.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses minimal cookies required for Google Analytics functionality. We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or any form of persistent user tracking.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We use Google Analytics for website analytics. Google may collect and process certain data as described in their Privacy Policy. We do not share any data with other third parties.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]">Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, because our calculator processes all data locally, there is no data transmission risk for calculator inputs.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through our <a href="/contact" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline" title="Contact DOGBREEDAGE">Contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
